<h1>Verify your email</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.display_name %>,</p>

<% if @contest %>
  <p>You're almost in <strong><%= @contest.name %></strong>! Confirm your email below —
     you'll land right back on the contest to finish your entry:</p>

  <p><%= link_to "Verify & finish my entry", @verify_url %></p>
<% else %>
  <p>Click the link below to verify the email address on your Turf Monster account:</p>

  <p><%= link_to "Verify my email", @verify_url %></p>
<% end %>

<p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
<p><%= @verify_url %></p>

<p>This link expires in 24 hours. If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this message.</p>

<p>— Turf Monster</p>
